00:06:22.510 --> 00:06:23.360
Rong...

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:29.430
Je veux que Rong revienne.

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:31.120
Je la veux de retour !

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:34.950
Pourquoi?

00:06:35.630 --> 00:06:38.360
